{% else -%}
pytest tests/
{% endif %}
```

## Commit Convention

```
feat: short description      # new feature (behind a flag)
fix: short description       # bug fix
test: short description      # adding/fixing tests
refactor: short description  # no behavior change
chore: short description     # tooling, deps, config
```

## Do Not

- Merge unfinished features directly visible to users — use flags.
- Create branches named after features — commit to main with flags.
- Skip tests when refactoring.
- Add error handling for impossible scenarios.
